exceptions.tactic: apply (invA_eqA_comp A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs).
exceptions.exn: In environment A : Set A0, A1 : A eqA : A -> A -> Prop plusA : A -> A -> A invA : A -> A minusA, multA : A -> A -> A divA : A -> forall b : A, ~ eqA b A0 -> A cs : CoefStructure A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA eqA_dec : forall a b : A, {eqA a b} + {~ eqA a b} eqA_trans := CoefStructure.eqA_trans A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs : Relation_Definitions.transitive A eqA eqA_sym := CoefStructure.eqA_sym A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs : Relation_Definitions.symmetric A eqA a, b : A Unable to unify "eqA (invA ?M1458) (invA ?M1459)" with "eqA (multA a (invA b)) (invA (multA a b))".

original: intros a b. apply (invA_eqA_comp A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs). apply multA_eqA_comp with (eqA (multA a A1)) (eqA (multA A1 b)). - apply eqA_sym. apply multA_A1_l. apply cs. - apply eqA_sym. apply multA_A1_l. apply cs.
